{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"95848499bb","title":"第一号通令","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c5e46306d3","index":0,"year":1966,"month":9,"day":10,"articleId":"95848499bb","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"红卫兵运动","id":"3be4d5766f","type":"主题"},{"name":"群众运动重要文献","id":"4bd6d6f93a","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"公安与法律","id":"53b954d860","type":"主题"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"1dfb1cf13c","name":"首都红卫兵纠察队（东城分队）"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"704b3e7238","type":"title","text":"第一号通令","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"95848499bb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a9de2ec645","type":"paragraph","text":"第一号通令","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"95848499bb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6a2f0d9e34","type":"paragraph","text":"首都红卫兵纠察队东城分队","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"95848499bb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7c9e0d924e","type":"paragraph","text":"1966.09.10","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"95848499bb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3aa6ce5022","type":"paragraph","text":"一、我们完全同意首都红卫兵纠察队西城区分队颁布的一至七号通令。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"95848499bb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8849c4ebf0","type":"paragraph","text":"二、由于东风市场的总部已经不能适应目前发展了的革命形势，所以经红卫兵纠察队东城分队讨论通过后，决定解散这一组织。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"95848499bb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"116d7e15b0","type":"paragraph","text":"三、为了谨防扒手，外地到北京的红卫兵如果没有证件，一律不准带袖章，如有违令者袖章一律没收。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"95848499bb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ecc90437ac","type":"paragraph","text":"四、关于外地来京的革命师生撤离北京的决定：","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"95848499bb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3350046314","type":"paragraph","text":"近日以来，伟大的无产阶级文化大革命的风暴席卷全国。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"95848499bb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5fb141d86a","type":"paragraph","text":"全国各地的红卫兵和革命师生为了寻求革命的真理，交流战斗的经验，将伟大的无产阶级文化大革命进行到底，冲破了重重的障碍，来到首都，来到毛主席的身边。对此我们举双手赞成，我们热烈地欢迎你们。但我们希望你们有组织地、有计划地、有领导地分期分批来，这样对革命更有利。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"95848499bb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5846b138e6","type":"paragraph","text":"当前，来到北京的部分同志缺乏健全的组织，缺乏统一的领导，给北京造成了比较严重的混乱现象。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"95848499bb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ee5f40e959","type":"paragraph","text":"例如：","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"95848499bb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c2c0078b27","type":"paragraph","text":"1．无组织的群众太多，使首都的秩序无法维持，极易被坏人钻空子。","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"95848499bb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"50c08b1ef2","type":"paragraph","text":"2．一部分人来历不明，少数组织混乱，成分不纯，安全保卫工作无法顺利进行。","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"95848499bb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cb62968b9a","type":"paragraph","text":"3．来京人过多，影响国庆招待外宾工作。","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"95848499bb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e00394b233","type":"paragraph","text":"这种混乱的状况，对于即将来临的国庆节十分不利，给准备工作带来了较多的困难。","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"95848499bb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"925c7c675c","type":"paragraph","text":"我们认为我国人民的国庆节是具有伟大的历史意义的节日。尤其是今年更具有特殊的意义，全世界革命的人民都在注视着我们。这次政治活动只能搞好，不能搞坏。","index":16,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"95848499bb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a1d729f8d3","type":"paragraph","text":"我们建议各地红卫兵和革命师生能在九月十五日以前暂时离开北京。希望红卫兵战士和一切有关单位协助我们完成这一任务，使首都“十一”庆祝活动正常进行。","index":17,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"95848499bb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a8b441aacb","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席说：“要提倡顾全大局。每一个党员，每一种局部工作，每一项言论或行动，都必须以全党利益为出发点，绝对不许可违反这个原则。”","index":18,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"95848499bb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6659efc492","type":"paragraph","text":"我们要站得高，看得远，顾全革命大局，而不是光顾眼前利益。最后，我们诚恳地告诫各地红卫兵和革命师生切记！切记！要顾全革命的大局！","index":19,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"95848499bb","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a67ad3a8d0","type":"paragraph","text":"（原载首都红卫兵纠察队（东城分队）《红卫兵战报》创刊号，1966年9月10日）","index":20,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"95848499bb","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}